多的助力、支持与尊重。 来源：中国妇女报"},"attached_info":"Cj8I9oqa5Y/W6as5EAMaCDc1MDAwMzEwIJbZ/40GMAM4iQJAC3IJNTA3MjM0MTI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"191 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-cace8ffa4a20251617d8d69cdc2ad8b7_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1639977060.092151","card_id":"Q_506756918","target":{"id":506756918,"title":"如何看待华为官宣 Harmony OS 2 正式版已全部上线完成？鸿蒙的战斗结束了吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/506756918","type":"question","created":1639744263,"answer_count":99,"follower_count":191,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5263,21576,59139,405190,604358],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I9oqa5Y/W6as5EAMaCDc0ODk0NDYwIIeG8o0GMAI4vwFADHIJNTA2NzU2OTE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"182 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-a5efea7573a3a9e346a8ea4643e8828d_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1639977060.092684","card_id":"Q_506110785","target":{"id":506110785,"title":"2021 年作为家长，你是如何平衡好「亲子陪伴」、「繁忙工作」和「自我提升」三者的关系？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/506110785","type":"question","created":1639526127,"answer_count":64,"follower_count":372,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1395,2623,4719,725166,1548596],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我和我先生都是重视亲子陪伴的践行者，同时也都是对自己工作有追求的中年人。 2022 年 1 月 1 日后，《家庭教育促进法》将正式实施，该法案强调了父母在家庭教育中的重要性，指出父母应当加强亲子陪伴。我们都很认同该法案的建议，但梦想很美好，现实却很无奈，对于大多数普通家庭来说，父母双方作为顶梁柱，总要忙于工作，甚至常常不得不在晚间和周末加班，同时，正值壮年的我们，也需要不断自我提升，才不至于被职场淘汰，被人取代。我和我先生也因为每天晚上陪伴幼儿园的孩子做手工、画画、阅读、拼玩具等，而不得不牺牲睡觉的时间来加班、学习、阅读和运动。所以问题就来了：一边是陪伴孩子，一边是繁忙的工作，还有一边是自我精进（包括学习提升和体育锻炼等），可时间只有那么多，我们要怎么才能找好一个平衡点，既不影响孩子的发展，也不耽误自己的人生？ 2021 年即将过去，回顾这一年，作为父母，我们一起经历了许多变化，从三孩及双减政策的落地，到孩子们成长的点滴。在这众多的变化之中，也有很多弥足珍贵的「未曾改变」，比如孩子们的好奇心，比如家长们对于教育的持续关注与讨论。 为了给养育一个更好的答案，@知乎亲子特别邀请 20 位母婴领域答主共同发起「为人父母这一年」系列有奖提问，让我们一起在不断地提问中，寻找答案。 点击详细规则，查看全部有奖提问：https://www.zhihu.com/xen/market/ecom-page/1451983889141501952"},"attached_info":"Cj8I9oqa5Y/W6as5EAMaCDc0NzUwNDkzIO/d5I0GMAM49AJADXIJNTA2MTEwNzg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"116 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-607a2549fba1aa66c07d4b4058c4bb16_1440w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1639977060.0935721","card_id":"Q_505682414","target":{"id":505682414,"title":"有人说「没有小米，也会有其他厂商把手机价格拉低」，你怎么看待这句话？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/505682414","type":"question","created":1639364548,"answer_count":100,"follower_count":113,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[488,890,25405],"comment_count":6,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I9oqa5Y/W6as5EAMaCDc0NjU1MTkxIMTv2o0GMAY4cUAOcgk1MDU2ODI0MTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"114 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-fcb254cb96eec00f52680ba8fe686a9b_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1639977060.0943215","card_id":"Q_507164798","target":{"id":507164798,"title":"如何看待中纪委网站评明星艺人翻车「立艺先要立德」？如何才能称为一个合格的文艺工作者？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/507164798","type":"question","created":1639920901,"answer_count":83,"follower_count":237,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1718,1793,105508,745368,1335576],"comment_count":9,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"【中纪委网站评明星艺人人设崩塌：立艺先要立德】 近期，“人设崩塌”再